    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>論文燃やされたからあんなこと言うなんて
やつあたりだよ……ひどい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It’s terrible to take out your anger just because your thesis was burned...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クル〜〜ルゥ〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuuuuuuruuuu~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、&lt;MEL&gt;が髪飾り全部捨てられたら
どうすんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, what if all your hair ornaments were thrown away, Mel?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38240</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かに落ち込むけど、
あんなこと言わないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I’d definitely be upset, but I wouldn’t say something like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>育てた鉢植えや花壇の花、
掘り返されたら？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What if the potted plants or flower beds you nurtured were dug up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それもイヤだよ、でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wouldn’t like that either, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ポエム書いたノート、
燃やされるとか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Or if the notebook where you wrote your poems was burned...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And that too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39448</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？
なんで、&lt;DIO&gt;、そのこと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...? Why do you know about that, Dio...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール〜？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuuruu~?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、やべっ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, crap...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_013_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどーいっ！！　見たの！
ちょっと！　待ちなさいっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's terrible!! You saw it! Hey! Wait!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <StructId>12</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
